Histogram of relative DNA content of nuclei isolated from the leaves of the new plant and related 
<taxonomicName class="Liliopsida" family="Zingiberaceae" genus="Hedychium" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Hedychium" order="Scitamineae" pageId="4" pageNumber="73" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
